						Basis recognized by different countries/regions varies, and common Legality Bases
						include the following types:
(1)
Obtaining
							Your
(i.e.,
the
Data Subject’s) Consent:
In case the following
						Legality Bases cannot be applied, we will seek your consent.
(2)
Necessity
							for Conclusion or Performance of Contract between You and Us:
For
						example, we need to process the corresponding personal information in order to
						perform the
IQIYI Service Agreement
and the
IQIYI VIP Member Service
							Agreement
, and provide our services to you.
(3)
Necessity
							for Performance of Our Legal Obligations
: For example, in
						accordance with the requirements of applicable laws and regulations, or the
						requirements of administrative and judicial authorities, We need to process the
						corresponding personal information in order to perform our legal obligations.
(4)
Necessity
							for Achievement of Our or Third Party's Legitimate Interests
: For
						example, we need to process the corresponding personal information in order to
						maintain the security and reliability of Our Services, as well as to implement
						legitimate interests such as marketing events.
2
How
							do We use your personal information
2.1
Purpose
							of using personal information
We usually use your personal information
						for the following purposes.
You have no legal or contractual obligation to
							provide us with your personal information, but in case you fail to provide the
							personal information required for specific features or services, you may not be
							able to use the corresponding features or services, provided that your use of
							other features or services will not be affected.
(1) Registration and management of
							account
You can create an IQIYI account on our
						website or application. We will use the
personal profile
							information
provided by you
(for specific
							explanation of data type, please refer to Section 1.1 hereof, and for specific
							explanation of other data type involved in the following sections, please also
							refer to Section 1.1 hereof)
to manage your account and provide
						you with a series of practical features.
You can perform various operations within
						your IQIYI account, such as enriching your profile information, purchasing VIP
						membership benefits, and adjusting personal settings (such as clarity, stream,
						channel, subtitle settings, and other default watching settings).
(2) Provision of audio/video
							related services
By using your
usage information
, We
						will provide you with a consistent playback experience and facilitate the
						viewing of your playback, download, collection, and other records.
For the purpose of allowing you to
						participate in platform interaction features (such as commenting on audio and
						video contents) and display other users' evaluation on audio and video contents
						to users, We need to use your
user-generated contents and some personal
							profile information (profile picture, and nickname)
.
In certain countries/regions, in
						accordance with the applicable laws and regulations, We may need to use your
personal
							profile information (age)
to verify whether you are of sufficient age to
						use Our Services.
(3) Provision of VIP membership
							benefits and paid services
Our Services are partly free and partly
						paid (such as watching of VIP episodes). We will use your
payment
							information
to achieve the purchase of membership benefits, provide you
						with the enjoyment of paid services, and ensure the security of transactions, which
						is crucial for us to provide you with this service. This includes but is not
						limited to sending the relevant membership benefits to you, providing you with
						proof of purchase and/or payment, and showing you the detailed information
						about your benefits.
(4) Management and operation of
							platform
Usually, We need to use your
communication
							information
and query your
personal profile information, usage
							information, and user-generated contents
in the system backend, so as to
						process and respond to your requests, questions, inquiries, feedback, and
						disputes.
For the purpose of managing our
						relationship with you and sending you the support messages related to Our
						Services (such as the start date of subscribing to our VIP membership service,
						reminder on expiration of VIP membership service, and reminder on security of
						account), We need to use your
personal profile information (email, and
							mobile phone number)
.
(5) Personalized display and
							recommendation
Personalized display of film/television
						contents and advertisement information you see in Our Services is called
						personalized recommendation. For the purpose of providing personalized
						recommendations to you, including providing, analyzing, managing, improving,
						optimizing, selecting, and broadcasting film/television contents and
						advertisement information, We will use the following personal information of
						you:
personal profile information (gender, birthday, and age) and
							information automatically collected by us.
(6) Marketing
For the purpose of publicizing and
						promoting Our Services, We may send you marketing messages and carry out
						marketing events on our own or through third parties in cooperation with us.
						For example, We may use your
personal profile information (email, and telephone
							number)
to send promotional emails and text messages about Our Services,
						new features, and promotional events, invite you to participate in our events,
						and distribute prizes/gifts from marketing events to you based on your
event
							information
.
We will also use your
personal profile
							information (gender, birthday, and age) and
information automatically
							collected by us
to provide you with a personalized experience in marketing
						events, evaluate and understand the effectiveness of our advertisement, and improve
						our advertisement delivery (including personalized advertisement).
(7) Maintenance of security and
							reliability
We need to use your
personal profile
							information (email, and telephone number), payment information, usage
							information, advertisement information, location information, and cookie
							information
to maintain the security and reliability of Our Services,
						detect potential security technology risks, and prevent, monitor, and
						investigate into possible illegal activities.
(8) Statistical analysis, improvement
							and optimization of Our Services
We may use the
information proactively
							provided by you,
information automatically collected by us, information
							from third parties,
and
publicly available information
for
						research, analysis, and statistics, so as to continuously improve and optimize
						Our Services. For example, We may conduct market research and trend analysis,
						comprehensively summarize and analyze the situation related to Our Services,
